  "stem": "<p>Let <math><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>16</mn><mi>x</mi></math> and <math><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>4</mn></math>. Which of the following expressions is equivalent to <math><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mfrac></math>, for <math><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>4</mn></math>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p><math><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></math></p>"
